Popular Mechanics September 2013 (USA)
English | 132 pages | PDF | 39.52 MB

Popular Mechanics helps you master the modern world, presenting trusted information about your home, your car, your technology and the world around you With tool tests, building projects, car reviews and more, PM shows the American man how to upgrade his life. Popular Mechanics is where innovation meets inspiration. Every issue includes tons of useful do-it-yourself tips and ideas, car reviews, and the latest tech, space, science news, and more.
